Package: shinyswarm
Type: Package
Title: Full-State Capture and Restore for Shiny Applications
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Iva", family = "Gunjaca", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "gunjaca.iva@gmail.com")
Description: Transport-agnostic full-state serialisation and restoration for
    Shiny applications. Captures both inputs and computed reactive values to a
    single JSON string and restores them later, guaranteeing exact
    reproducibility without recomputation. The library produces and consumes
    JSON only; how it is transmitted or persisted (REST, Kafka, Redis, file,
    database) is left to the caller. Typed wrappers handle file references and
    arbitrary binary R objects. Prototype accompanying the ShinySwarm thesis.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    base64enc
Suggests:
    shiny,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
